1) Pick a content type (choose based on interest + effort)
AI-assisted explainer videos — short topic explainers (science, tech, history) using AI scripts, voice, and visuals. Good for evergreen growth.
AI-generated storytelling — short fiction, audio dramas, or narrated micro-stories created with AI writing tools and TTS voices.
AI tutorials & walkthroughs — teach AI tools (how to use ChatGPT, image-gen tips, prompt engineering). Great if you like teaching.
