Video 1 — Introduction: What the channel is and one quick demo (3–5 min).
Video 2 — Tutorial: How to generate a character in Midjourney (6–10 min).
Video 3 — Speed-create: From prompt to final image with voiceover (short or long).
Video 4 — Tips & mistakes beginners make (listicle, 6–8 min).
For each: write scripts with AI, record TTS or voice, add visuals, publish, then iterate based on analytics.
